OL,3,CFlu cases in Scotland increase as flu
OL,4,Cjab struggles to cope with new variant
OL,6,FThe number of flu cases in Scotland
OL,7,Frose by 45% in a week, as this year's
OL,8,Fflu jab struggles to cope with a new
OL,9,Finfluenza variant.
OL,11,FIn the week ending 23 November, the
OL,12,Fnumber of laboratory-confirmed cases
OL,13,Frose to 805 from 555, while the
OL,14,Finfection rate increased from 10 per
OL,15,F100,000 people to 14.5 per 100,000,
OL,16,Faccording to figures from Public
OL,17,FHealth Scotland.
