OL,3,CFlu cases in Scotland increase as flu
OL,4,Cjab struggles to cope with new variant
OL,6,FThe proportion of positive test
OL,7,Fresults also increased, from 11% to
OL,8,F15.8%, whilst hospital admissions
OL,9,Freached 391, up from 279 the week
OL,10,Fbefore.
OL,12,FNHS Borders has in the past weeks
OL,13,Fclosed certain rooms and bays in wards
OL,14,Fas a precaution.
OL,16,FMeanwhile Dr Kenneth Donaldson,
OL,17,FMedical Director at Dumfries and
OL,18,FGalloway Royal Infirmary, says the
OL,19,Fsituation is particularly bad at his
OL,20,Fhospital.
