OL,3,CFlu cases in Scotland increase as flu
OL,4,Cjab struggles to cope with new variant
OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV Border, he said:
OL,7,F"We've seen a doubling of the number
OL,8,Fof positive flu cases in D&G and we
OL,9,Fhave seen that surge of patients being
OL,10,Fadmitted to hospital.
OL,12,F"We're asking the public to be aware,
OL,13,Fand try to take measures: wash hands,
OL,14,Fand try and distance as much as
OL,15,Fpossible."
OL,17,FThe infirmary has now taken action to
OL,18,Ftry and stop the spread, including
OL,19,Frestricting visiting hours and having
OL,20,Fclinical staff wear masks.
