OL,3,CFlu cases in Scotland increase as flu
OL,4,Cjab struggles to cope with new variant
OL,6,FDr Donaldson said: "If you have
OL,7,Fsymptoms, don't come into hospital,
OL,8,Funless you're needing clinical input.
OL,10,F"We've restricted visiting (at the
OL,11,Fhospital) - people can still visit,
OL,12,Fbut they will have to phone in advance
OL,13,Fand wear a mask in clinical areas."
OL,15,FPublic Health Scotland figures show
OL,16,Fthat all age groups have been affected
OL,17,Fby the flu at unprecedented levels for
OL,18,Fthis time of year.
