OL,3,CFlu cases in Scotland increase as flu
OL,4,Cjab struggles to cope with new variant
OL,6,FIt is thought that a new mutation of
OL,7,Finfluenza, known as H3N2, has reduced
OL,8,Fthe efficacy of this year's flu
OL,9,Fvaccination, making the strain easier
OL,10,Fto catch and spread.
OL,12,FThis strain also seems to cause more
OL,13,Fsevere illness in those infected,
OL,14,Ffurther compounding the problem.
